<template><div><h1 id="use-window-size-介绍" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#use-window-size-介绍"><span>use-window-size 介绍</span></a></h1>
<p><code v-pre>use-window-size</code> 用于获取窗口的尺寸。它返回一个包含窗口宽度和高度的响应式对象。</p>
